Lines: a very close game i say. if you do not mind, i shall be taking my reward...
[i]as the dealer clicks his fingers together, pain shoots through you as you look down to not find your left arm.
[i]at this moment, you realise the stakes were real all along.
a fine addition to my collection. now now, i will give you an opportunity to get it back.
although the forfit will be your soul...
